Text:
"Zensiert in dem Sinne das 1 bis 3 Balken etwas verdecken sollten, schaut euch die Screens an und entscheidet selber."
translates to 
"Mark something in the sense the 1 to 3 bar should cover, the Screens looks at you and decides for itself."



WTF?????????
not really. "censored" means that 1-3 dots are supposed to cover something, look at the screens and decide for yourselves.
